file.name: array-example.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 0.0.0
  title: Array mock test
paths:
  /:
    get:
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/User'
                example:
                  - id: 1
                    name: Arthur Dent
                  - id: 2
                    name: Ford Prefect
components:
  schemas:
    User:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          example: 0
        name:
          type: string
          example: Marvin
